      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Abaye, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"121\" data-full-name=\"Abaye\" data-name-he=\"אביי\">אַבָּיֵי</span>: פְּלִיג בְּבָרַיְיתָא, דְּתַנְיָא: קִבֵּל בִּשְׂמֹאל",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "פָּסוּל, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">וְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> מַכְשִׁיר; זָרַק בִּשְׂמֹאל פָּסוּל, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47036\">וְרַבִּי</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\" data-crossline-group=\"name-ref-crossline-47036\">שִׁמְעוֹן</span> מַכְשִׁיר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאֶלָּא, הָא דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span>: ״יָד״ ״יָד״",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לִקְמִיצָה, לְמָה לִי? מִכְּהוּנָּה נָפְקָא! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>חַד לְקוֹמֶץ,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְחַד לְקִידּוּשׁ קוֹמֶץ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">לְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> דְּלָא בָּעֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קִידּוּשׁ קוֹמֶץ, וּלְמַאן דְּאָמַר נָמֵי דְּבָעֵי קִידּוּשׁ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קוֹמֶץ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">לְרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>, וּבִשְׂמֹאל אַכְשׁוֹרֵי מַכְשַׁר –",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״יָד״ ״יָד״ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabba I, fourth-generation Amora\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rabba I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">דְּרָבָא</span> לְמָה לִי? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אִי לִקְמִיצָה גּוּפַהּ, אַלִּיבָּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">דְּרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda, son of Rabbi, first-generation II Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1441\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda, son of Rabbi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה בריה דרבי חייא\">מִדְּרַבִּי יְהוּדָה בְּרֵיהּ דְּרַבִּי חִיָּיא</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נָפְקָא, דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yehuda, son of Rabbi, first-generation II Amora\" data-authority-id=\"1441\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehuda, son of Rabbi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהודה בריה דרבי חייא\">רַבִּי יְהוּדָה בְּרֵיהּ דְּרַבִּי חִיָּיא</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַאי טַעְמָא <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">דְּרַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span>? דְּאָמַר קְרָא: ״קֹדֶשׁ קָדָשִׁים",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הִיא כַּחַטָּאת וְכָאָשָׁם״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בָּא לְעוֹבְדָהּ בַּיָּד –",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עוֹבְדָהּ בְּיָמִין, כְּחַטָּאת; בָּא לְעוֹבְדָהּ בִּכְלִי –",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "עוֹבְדָהּ בִּשְׂמֹאל, כְּאָשָׁם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>לֹא נִצְרְכָא אֶלָּא לְקוֹמֶץ",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּמִנְחַת חוֹטֵא, סָלְקָא דַּעְתָּךְ אָמֵינָא: הוֹאִיל",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai, fifth-generation Tanna\" data-authority-id=\"2830\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Shimon ben Yoḥai\" data-name-he=\"רבי שמעון בן יוחאי\">רַבִּי שִׁמְעוֹן</span> שֶׁלֹּא יְהֵא קׇרְבָּנוֹ מְהוּדָּר,",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כִּי קָמֵיץ לַהּ נָמֵי בִּשְׂמֹאל תִּתַּכְשַׁר, קָמַשְׁמַע לַן. ",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-vilna-piska\" data-sugya-kind=\"vilna-piska\" data-sugya-id=\"15\" data-raw-symbol=\"׃\">׃</span> <span class=\"sugya-marker sugya-marker-steinsaltz\" data-sugya-kind=\"steinsaltz\" data-sugya-id=\"30\" data-sentence-id=\"7\" data-steinsaltz-label=\"א\">§</span> <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>קָמַץ וְעָלָה בְּיָדוֹ צְרוֹר, אוֹ גַרְגֵּר מֶלַח,",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
